  <summary date="2017-12-07T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Supporting Children of the National Guard and Reserve Act

This bill amends the Elementary and Secondary Education Act of 1965 to include students with a parent who serves in the reserve component of the Armed Forces under the military student identifier program. Thus, schools must assign those students identification numbers that allow the schools to monitor their achievement on academic assessments.</summary>
